' NOTES
' ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
note right of appState
  [State 5.6 - Authenticated]
  After Seq 4.1 (Login-Password):
    UserBLL.LoginAsync("tuyethan", password) => true
    UserRepository.GetByUsernameAsync() => UserDTO(U03)
    SecurityHelper.VerifyPassword(pw, hash) => true
    AppState.Instance.CurrentUser <= UserDTO(U03)
    SystemAuditHelper.LogAsync("LOGIN","Users","U03")
end note

note right of contract1
  [State 5.1 - ContractStatus.Active = 0]
  After Seq 4.3 (Create Contract):
    ContractValidator.ValidateAndThrow(ContractDto) => OK
    ContractRepository.AddContractAsync(ContractDto)
    AiIntegrationService.PredictRenewal(
      31000000, "FoodAndBeverage", 2, 0) => score=0.78
    SystemAuditHelper.LogAsync(
      "CREATE_CONTRACT","Contracts","HD-0001")
  ---
  CreatedBy = "U06" (Minhkhoa - Sales)
  [Seed: CASE WHEN @i%2=0 THEN 'U03' ELSE 'U06'; i=1 odd => U06]
end note

note bottom of aiResult
  AiIntegrationService (singleton, no interface):
    Model: ML.NET ITransformer (trained on CustomerFeedbacks)
    Input: ContractRenewalInput {
      TotalValue=31000000, Industry="FoodAndBeverage",
      ResponseTime=2, Violations=0, Frequency=5 }
    Output: ContractRenewalPrediction {
      Score=0.78, PredictedLabel=true }
  Shown via DashboardUC and ContractListUC
end note

